<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7917224>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. New and poorly known grylloblattids: (A, B) Iphikozulu kwayayaensis Aristov & Mostovski, gen. et sp. n., holotype, forewing impression (A) and details of its venation (B); (C, D) Neoliomopterum picturatum Riek, 1976, holotype NMSA 910, forewing impression (C) and details of its venation (D). Scale bars 5 mm in Figs 2A, 2B, and 2 mm in Figs 2C, 2D." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7917224/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

